_sText:
This map is a pretty basic fightyard with a buy zone. Map supports 32 players and is best played with large groups of people (or bots). Feel free to use on any public or clan servers. 

I would appreciate any input for improvements or new ideas. 

If you decide to edit this map in any way please credit Nalthador and when your done send me a copy!

happy shooting!
 -Nalthador
